message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product for $200. I believe it will be very valuable for you.
I'm interested in the product, but $200 is a bit steep for me. I was thinking more along the lines of $120.
I understand your position, Bob. How about we meet in the middle at $160?
I appreciate your willingness to compromise, but I'm still a bit short on budget. How about we meet at $140?
